02:04:45.740 --> 02:04:49.600
The economist has a little of his own view.

02:04:55.550 --> 02:04:58.350
Alternative costs are

02:04:58.350 --> 02:05:01.010
economic costs.

02:05:01.010 --> 02:05:04.310
They represent the value of

02:05:04.310 --> 02:05:07.410
the goods that could be obtained

02:05:07.410 --> 02:05:12.150
by the most profitable of

02:05:12.150 --> 02:05:17.340
all alternative ways of

02:05:17.340 --> 02:05:20.020
using limited resources.

02:05:20.120 --> 02:05:22.540
I am afraid it is not very clear, but it can be easier.

02:05:22.540 --> 02:05:26.020
In practical calculations,

02:05:26.020 --> 02:05:29.740
economic costs include, in addition

02:05:29.740 --> 02:05:33.520
to the explicit or accounting

02:05:33.520 --> 02:05:37.300
costs, also the implicit

02:05:37.300 --> 02:05:39.280
costs.

02:05:39.300 --> 02:05:41.740
Can we write that economic

02:05:41.740 --> 02:05:46.640
