02:05:46.800 --> 02:05:50.140
Accounting costs plus some other

02:05:50.140 --> 02:05:53.020
unclear costs.

02:05:54.460 --> 02:06:00.840
What is accounting costs?

02:06:00.940 --> 02:06:01.940
I have already said.

02:06:03.260 --> 02:06:05.920
It is not clear what implicit costs are.

02:06:06.020 --> 02:06:06.940
We read.

02:06:08.040 --> 02:06:11.840
The implicit costs are the

02:06:11.840 --> 02:06:15.500
amount of incomes of the

02:06:15.500 --> 02:06:20.140
company on its own resources.

02:06:20.620 --> 02:06:24.000
It is about the income that the

02:06:24.000 --> 02:06:27.640
management of the company could

02:06:27.640 --> 02:06:36.680
get by using its resources not in

02:06:36.680 --> 02:06:41.260
this business, but somehow differently.

02:06:41.360 --> 02:06:43.800
Let us find out.

02:06:43.900 --> 02:06:48.970
Imagine that you have started your own

02:06:48.970 --> 02:06:49.670
business.

02:06:49.770 --> 02:06:51.830
You come into this business not

02:06:51.830 --> 02:06:53.230
with empty hands.

02:06:53.690 --> 02:06:59.180
What did you bring with you?

02:06:59.280 --> 02:07:02.280
Maybe a lot of

02:07:02.280 --> 02:07:04.380
money.

02:07:05.420 --> 02:07:10.980
Let's say 100 rubles.

02:07:11.080 --> 02:07:13.040
Could you use this

02:07:13.040 --> 02:07:15.980
capital as an alternative?

02:07:16.080 --> 02:07:20.580
Of course could.

02:07:20.680 --> 02:07:22.580
What is the easiest way

02:07:22.580 --> 02:07:23.640
to use that money?

02:07:23.740 --> 02:07:28.240
You could put them in the bank.

02:07:29.610 --> 02:07:31.490
You would get a percentage.

02:07:31.590 --> 02:07:33.610
If you invest that money in your

02:07:36.030 --> 02:07:40.850
own company, you have lost that percentage.

02:07:40.950 --> 02:07:46.050
And this unreceived percentage will

02:07:46.050 --> 02:07:52.520
enter the firm's implicit costs.

02:07:52.620 --> 02:07:55.340
Well, let's say you invested 100

02:07:55.340 --> 02:07:57.020
rubles in your business.

02:07:57.840 --> 02:08:00.380
You had to close your

02:08:00.380 --> 02:08:02.980
bank account.

02:08:02.980 --> 02:08:08.260
You have lost 10% of your invested

02:08:08.260 --> 02:08:08.920
money.

02:08:22.740 --> 02:08:24.540
I for simplicity assume that the

02:08:24.540 --> 02:08:27.620
bank pays on deposits also 10%.

02:08:27.620 --> 02:08:33.070
So, the implicit cost that these

02:08:33.070 --> 02:08:34.390
funds you got as if free, but

02:08:34.390 --> 02:08:36.790
that does not mean that their

02:08:36.790 --> 02:08:39.190
use should be taken into account.

02:08:39.610 --> 02:08:41.630
So you invested 100 rubles,

02:08:41.990 --> 02:08:45.250
lost 10% on those funds, which

02:08:45.510 --> 02:08:46.970
you could get if you kept that

02:08:46.970 --> 02:08:48.410
money in the bank.

02:08:48.950 --> 02:08:50.510
And accordingly, in the implicit

02:08:50.510 --> 02:08:52.290
costs will include this unreceived

02:08:52.290 --> 02:08:53.890
percentage of 10 rubles.

02:08:55.110 --> 02:08:56.450
and further.

02:08:57.250 --> 02:08:58.710
In order to start your business,

02:08:58.710 --> 02:09:03.630
you had to leave your job.

02:09:04.710 --> 02:09:06.970
You probably worked for hiring before.

02:09:07.590 --> 02:09:08.770
So you lost?

02:09:10.370 --> 02:09:11.910
The wage.

02:09:12.450 --> 02:09:16.610
Unreceived wages will also be included

02:09:16.610 --> 02:09:19.450
in the firm's implicit costs.

02:09:20.270 --> 02:09:23.170
Let's say, by hiring, you

02:09:23.170 --> 02:09:24.710
earned 200 rubles.

02:09:25.170 --> 02:09:28.230
When you start your business, you lose

02:09:28.290 --> 02:09:29.730
those 200 rubles.

02:09:29.970 --> 02:09:31.930
These 200 rubles of unreceived

02:09:31.930 --> 02:09:34.370
salary economists include in the implicit

02:09:34.370 --> 02:09:37.510
costs of your company.

02:09:37.850 --> 02:09:39.910
I write.

02:09:39.910 --> 02:09:45.630
Unpaid salary.

02:09:46.790 --> 02:09:47.510
How many were there?

02:09:47.550 --> 02:09:49.730
20 rubles, I would say.

02:09:49.990 --> 02:09:51.950
Unpaid salary.

02:09:52.370 --> 02:09:54.930
Another assumption.

02:09:55.250 --> 02:09:57.530
Suppose for your business, you have turned

02:09:57.530 --> 02:10:15.520
your apartment into an office or a

02:10:15.520 --> 02:10:16.100
warehouse.

