How do you estimate your losses?

02:10:19.820 --> 02:10:24.190
You could provide this apartment

02:10:24.190 --> 02:10:26.330
for your business, you lost

02:10:26.330 --> 02:10:28.570
those 20 rubles.

02:10:29.070 --> 02:10:35.910
So, the unreceived rent is

02:10:35.910 --> 02:10:38.670
also legally included in the implicit

02:10:38.670 --> 02:10:41.050
costs.

02:10:41.150 --> 02:10:44.470
Unreceived rent is 20 rubles.

02:10:45.770 --> 02:10:46.870
Well well well.

02:10:47.410 --> 02:10:50.210
Summarizing all these lost income,

02:10:50.210 --> 02:10:59.330
we get the implicit costs of the company.

02:11:00.610 --> 02:11:03.990
We got 50 rubles.

02:11:05.310 --> 02:11:08.030
It turns out that the total

02:11:08.030 --> 02:11:10.570
