02:11:13.230 --> 02:11:20.110
costs of 50, and that 250

02:11:20.110 --> 02:11:22.090
rubles.

02:11:22.190 --> 02:11:23.790
But now we have to answer the most

02:11:23.790 --> 02:11:25.190
important question.

02:11:26.270 --> 02:11:28.130
Why are economists original?

02:11:29.130 --> 02:11:31.690
For what reason they have invented

02:11:31.690 --> 02:11:33.870
in addition to the explicit

02:11:33.870 --> 02:11:35.750
or accounting costs, which are

02:11:35.750 --> 02:11:38.310
obvious to all, some implicit

02:11:38.310 --> 02:11:40.890
costs, which, I will repeat,

02:11:40.890 --> 02:11:44.330
the firm does not even pay anyone.

02:11:46.220 --> 02:11:50.900
The implicit costs are those income that

02:11:51.480 --> 02:11:55.140
entrepreneurs have lost by investing their

02:11:56.460 --> 02:11:59.580
