So you have taxes in your

02:14:52.250 --> 02:14:52.790
pocket.

02:14:52.790 --> 02:14:53.650
I don't take, of course.

02:14:54.210 --> 02:14:55.210
40 rubles

02:14:56.230 --> 02:14:59.370
So you just do not have a profitable

02:14:59.370 --> 02:15:02.470
