Please look at the slide.

02:27:14.140 --> 02:27:17.900
FC is fixed cost.

02:27:19.020 --> 02:27:21.740
VC is variable cost, variable

02:27:22.000 --> 02:27:23.020
cost.

02:27:23.800 --> 02:27:25.820
The total cost is TC.

02:27:26.280 --> 02:27:29.560
Total costs of the company.

02:27:32.120 --> 02:27:35.800
It is also important to know

02:27:35.800 --> 02:27:40.940
the unit cost or average cost.

02:27:41.140 --> 02:27:44.600
The average constant cost is indicated

02:27:44.600 --> 02:27:46.580
by the letter AFC.

02:27:47.320 --> 02:27:48.560
Look at the slide.

02:27:48.800 --> 02:27:50.880
These are fixed costs

02:27:50.980 --> 02:27:53.000
per unit of production.

02:27:53.360 --> 02:27:57.820
AFC is equal to FC constant

02:27:57.820 --> 02:27:59.780
cost divided

02:27:59.780 --> 02:28:01.340
by Q.

