02:34:47.500 --> 02:34:49.780
considered to be a variable factor.

02:34:51.870 --> 02:34:56.530
Accordingly, capital costs in the

02:34:56.530 --> 02:34:58.230
short period are fixed costs,

02:34:58.230 --> 02:35:01.590
and labor costs in the short

02:35:01.590 --> 02:35:04.330
period are variable costs.

02:35:07.320 --> 02:35:09.880
Let's see what the costs

02:35:09.880 --> 02:35:13.400
