02:39:10.130 --> 02:39:13.310
with the volume of sales, that is, it grows

02:39:13.310 --> 02:39:15.050
with the volume of production.

02:39:15.550 --> 02:39:17.890
Therefore, for trade, the purchase

02:39:17.890 --> 02:39:20.890
