03:28:56.170 --> 03:28:58.040
term average costs than those

03:28:58.050 --> 03:29:00.440
that would have been

03:29:00.450 --> 03:29:03.580
created if two or more

03:29:03.590 --> 03:29:06.560
companies were in the

03:29:06.570 --> 03:29:08.320
market instead.

03:29:10.500 --> 03:29:13.520
What is the nature of

03:29:13.530 --> 03:29:14.760
natural monopoly?

03:29:16.540 --> 03:29:20.310
The fact that its special monopoly

03:29:20.320 --> 03:29:24.590
position is not based on

03:29:24.600 --> 03:29:27.870
administrative resources, not

03:29:27.880 --> 03:29:29.690
on some other factors that can be

03:29:31.720 --> 03:29:34.590
eliminated in principle, and

03:29:34.600 --> 03:29:38.290
its monopoly position is based

03:29:38.300 --> 03:29:41.230
