03:33:31.870 --> 03:33:36.450
The unit cost of products will increase.

03:33:36.750 --> 03:33:39.050
This is a natural monopoly.

03:33:39.470 --> 03:33:42.090
I repeat, a natural monopoly is

03:33:42.100 --> 03:33:46.590
a firm whose monopoly position

03:33:46.600 --> 03:33:47.590
is based on cost

03:33:49.590 --> 03:33:52.060
advantages and is associated

03:33:52.070 --> 03:33:55.040
